Criminal Records Review Act
Criminal Record Check Fee Regulation
[includes amendments up to B.C. Reg. 214/2013, November 30, 2013]

Fee payment
1   (1)The fee payable for a criminal record check is $28.

(2)The acceptable methods of paying the fee for a criminal record check are certified cheque, money order and credit card.

[am. B.C. Reg. 214/2013, s. (b).]

[Provisions relevant to the enactment of this regulation: Criminal Records Review Act, R.S.B.C. 1996, c. 86, section 29 (2) (e) and (f)]
